{"id": "art-4713", "label": "Art. 4713", "title": "Art. 4713: Consiliere", "slug": "art-4713", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1208109585\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1638\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1208109585\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><u><span style='color:#569748'>Art. 47<sup>13</sup>:\nConsiliere </span></u></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2081507775\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1637\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2081507775\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(1)Consilierul de etic&#259;, desemnat potrivit\ndispozi&#355;iilor art. 451 din prezentul cod, asigur&#259; îndrumarea\npersoanelor prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup> alin. (1) din oficiu, la data\nprelu&#259;rii mandatului sau a func&#355;iei, &#351;i la cerere, pe toat&#259;\ndurata exercit&#259;rii mandatului sau a func&#355;iei.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_32265416\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1636\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_32265416\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Îndrumarea\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) se realizeaz&#259; prin:</b></span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1751396144\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1635\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1751396144\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>a)informarea persoanelor prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup>\nalin. (1) în leg&#259;tur&#259; cu cadrul legal &#351;i metodologic aplicabil\nnormelor de etic&#259; &#351;i conduit&#259; pentru membrii Guvernului, alte\npersoane care ocup&#259; func&#355;ii de demnitate public&#259; la nivelul\nadministra&#355;iei publice centrale. Informarea se realizeaz&#259; din oficiu\n&#351;i la cerere;</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1053577572\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1634\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1053577572\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>b)consilierea persoanelor prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup>\nalin. (1) în leg&#259;tur&#259; cu normele de etic&#259; &#351;i conduit&#259;\nprivind cadourile, transparen&#355;a intereselor în exercitarea\natribu&#355;iilor &#351;i programele de formare &#351;i perfec&#355;ionare din\ncuprinsul prezentului capitol. Consilierea se realizeaz&#259; la cerere.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_819784464\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1633\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_819784464\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(3)Consilierul de etic&#259; are obliga&#355;ia de a\np&#259;stra confiden&#355;ialitatea cu privire la datele, informa&#355;iile\n&#351;i con&#355;inutul consilierii oferite în condi&#355;iile alin. (2) lit.\nb).</span></u></p>"}